UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.IconIdentifier.D: Assigns an icon to the HUD icon to make it identifiable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.BallLogoBrightne: Determines how bright the logo of the ball appears.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Gravity.Descript: Determines how fast the ball falls to the ground.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.DamageImpulseFor: Determines how much horizontal force is applied when the ball takes damage.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PlayerImpulseFor: Determines how much horizontal force the player will apply when hitting the ball with their body.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PickaxeImpulseFo: Determines how much horizontal force the player will apply when hitting the ball with their pickaxe.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.DamageImpulseFor: Determines how much vertical force is applied when the ball takes damage.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PlayerImpulseFor: Determines how much vertical force the player will apply when hitting the ball with their body.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PickaxeImpulseFo: Determines how much vertical force the player will apply when hitting the ball with their pickaxe.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.BallRoughness.De: Determines how rough or smooth the ball appears.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.BallMetalness.De: Determines how shiny the ball appears.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.HUD Icon.Descrip: Determines if the HUD icon will be displayed for this device.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.EliminatePlayerW: Determines if the ball should eliminate a player when it touches them.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PlayerKnockbackF: Determines the amount of force applied to the player when the ball hits them.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.AngularDamping.D: Determines the ball's resistance to rotational movement.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.LinearDamping.De: Determines the ball's resitance to translational movement.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.SpawnedBallColor: Determines the base color of the ball.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.BallSize.Descrip: Determines the diameter of the ball
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Hide HUD Icon At: Determines the distance at which the HUD icon will stop being visible.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.PlayerForceMulti: Determines the force multiplier applied to all impact types. Has no effect on individually modified impulse forces.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Enabled During P: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Respawn Delay.De: Determines the length of time the spawner will wait to spawn a new ball after the previous one has been destroyed.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Mass.Description: Determines the mass of the spawned ball.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.MaximumDistanceR: Determines the maximum distance the ball can be from the device before respawning.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.HUD Text Size.De: Determines the size of text displayed on the HUD icon.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Ball Type.Descri: Determines the type of ball to spawn.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Requires Line Of: Determines whether direct lineof sight is required to see the HUD icon.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Base Visible Dur: Determines whether the base is visible during the game.
Determines which team can see the HUD icon.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Friendly Team.De: Determines which team(if any) sees the HUD indicator as Friendly.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Disable.Descript: Disables the device and despawns the ball.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Enable.Descripti: Enables the device and spawns, or respawns, the ball.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Friendly Icon Te: Specifies text to be displayed on the HUD icon for friendly players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Hostile Icon Tex: Specifies text to be displayed on the HUD icon for hostile players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Neutral Icon Tex: Specifies text to be displayed on the HUD icon for neutral players.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.When Player Touc: Triggers when the ball touches a player for the first time after not touching that player.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.When Ground Touc: Triggers when the ball touches the ground for the first time after not hitting the ground.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Display Distance: When showing as a HUD Element, also display the distance between the associated object and the player.
When showing as a HUD Element, clamp the rendering position to be within the screen.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_BallSpawner_V3_C.Show Offscreen A: When showing as a HUD Element, when the actual rendering position is offscreen show an arrow pointing in the offscreen direction.
